            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>警惕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E5%BD%93%E6%88%90%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E8%83%83%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E5%BD%93%E6%88%90%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E8%83%83%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃癌早期症状不明显易被当成慢性胃病#</span></a>】胃癌在我国是最常见的消化道肿瘤之一，其演变过程较长，有时甚至可达10年以上。胃癌早期症状不明显，易被忽视，但若及时发现，根治性切除后的复发率很低。因此，重视早期筛查、改变不良的饮食和生活方式非常关键。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些人属于胃癌高危人群#</span></a>？如何远离癌症？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E6%A6%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E6%A6%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳发布最新肿瘤排行榜#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4891798078947373" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hd3kd76gwxj620014iqv502.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/CFH4jR4llx084KW51r8401041200L5co0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681967968&amp;ssig=bVDcoyOiBn&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UzBigQkilx084KW1llmw01041200p4xJ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681967968&amp;ssig=eAowaQgwGc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/qghcP9qclx084KW0q8pq01041200fZmy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681967968&amp;ssig=lJ%2BopPvc%2Bc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4891798078947373&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
